data.AA: International Telephone Access Code - Dialing Code required to call another country in addition to the number
data.AC: Message Only Voice Number - Telephone number which provides automated messages only
data.AU: Defense Switched Network - Department of Defense telecommunications system and successor of the Automatic Voice Network (AUTOVON)
data.BT: BTX Number - German communications number for on-line service provided through the Deutsche Bundespost
data.DN: Defense Data Network (DDN) - Department of Defense (DoD) data communications system
data.SP: Showing Phone - Phone number to call for information about a property showing
data.TN: Teletex Number - Teletex is specific type of Telex service provided by Deutsche Bundespost
